## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

You can bundle the Dynatrace Ruxit Agent with the [Java buildpack version 3.8](https://network.pivotal.io/products/buildpacks) available on PivNet (as of June 2016). Dynatrace recommends that you use the latest version of the Ruxit Agent. Overwrite the default version with `version: 1.+`. 

Future releases of Dynatrace Ruxit for PCF will support Node.js and PHP buildpacks.

